Posted By: Brian Collie
I've been making good progress on the HOFs and now want to shift attention to the commons.  Looking for a nice lot of PSA 4 commons (PSA 5 if the price is right) - preferably no creases. To keep costs down I'm mostly interested in Piedmont and SC backs.  However, I wouldn't mind a few of the less common backs.  

If interested I have plenty of unopened wax from the 90s I would be happy to include as trade.

Please email me if interested.

Thanks so much.

Brian

Posted By: Jim
What are you paying per PSA 4?

Posted By: Brian Collie
Thanks for the reply.  Price depends on the overall condition and appearance - in the range of $45-$55.  Send me an email if you have some cards your interested in selling.  Thanks,
